{"tid":1442822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於元朗打人 前線職員的少少睇法","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:29:14.000Z","uid":197815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2b3128ef6ea3b778934ba1bf8f73236e62039c","tid":1442822,"uid":197815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"最近仲有人講點解元朗站個司機唔閂門<br />\n又或者點解啲白衫會入到嚟<br />\n作為曾經做過西鐵線嘅職員<br />\n我想一一解釋清楚<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 點解個司機唔閂門</span></span></strong><br />\n因為係車箱內 如果有乘客噤咗緊急制<br />\n司機係閂唔到車門同幕門<br />\n原則上係可以開鎖匙閂幕門<br />\n但始終今次係特別情況<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.點解白衫會入到閘打人</span></span></strong><br />\n好遺憾的係<br />\n基於港鐵將西鐵綫的客務中心外判咗俾其他公司<br />\n唔知係擔方便定其他原因<br />\n將緊急出口門上面的閃燈同響聲掩咗<br />\n同時將系統個警告掩咗<br />\n導致啲白衫人入咗Paid位而無人知<br />\n<br />\n此外,西鐵線的閘機本身係比較矮及容易受物件影響<br />\n故此亦容易俾白衫擋閘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 點解個司機唔答得問題</span></span></strong><br />\n只可以咁講 公司規定係唔可以答其他與事件/意外的<br />\n相關問題"},{"pid":"15582271118522822665d10b2fa7a9887feaec9f","tid":1442822,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6b1217d464d3cc6d47b90d3545a0a101381dbe","tid":1442822,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐怖襲擊警黑勾結<br />\n發生至今22日<br />\n無白衣人被起訴<br />\n無高官問責下台<br />\n無警隊高層需要革職<br />\n無警隊指揮官需要革職<br />\n無執勤警員需要革職<br />\n民建聯、工聯會縱容包庇"},{"pid":"7b66a3da34f572499922e3b3417a44f8466259e0","tid":1442822,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"721 官警黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a8516389375a268653f72d06f3334cecbef252","tid":1442822,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"幫你總結<br />\n<br />\n推得一乾二淨 我都無咩好總結<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ecead924d8497b59ef8fc7b55fe6d70d6399bc","tid":1442822,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"你咪ON9<br />\n道門明明閂過<br />\n之後再開返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a97ee7182e1aff5dafa4dc7b1fb0e4df34f3eb0","tid":1442822,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"自己起呢條友底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b89a5a50f5b50be935b886bac82651d3a0bb785","tid":1442822,"uid":245726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"請善用不推文同起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此po議員！"},{"pid":"37efcdd098c7dabbce76f76cea7b38678b988cf2","tid":1442822,"uid":197815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ecead924d8497b59ef8fc7b55fe6d70d6399bc","tid":1442822,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"你咪ON9<br />\n道門明明閂過<br />\n之後再開返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"你唔Reset 隻PAD又點閂門"}]}